PS - Though oil bath is considered the best technology, Walter at Bus
Boys did tell me that at the age of our oil baths, the innards are
collapsing and rendering them unserviceable. If left standing too
long, old dried crud can also form inside that will resist cleaning.
Just for grins try removing it for a brief run around the block and
see if the rich running stops.

John

